sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant OP as Operator
  participant API as API
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant WK as Worker

  OP->>API: POST /admin/model-provider {provider, reason}
  API->>API: reject if the provider's key isn't configured (400)
  API->>DB: audit switch_model_provider → set_active_provider
  API->>API: ProviderResolver.invalidate() — instant in this process
  Note over WK: Worker resolver picks up the change within the ~10s TTL
